Dependencies:
	CMake 3.0.x
	wxWidgets 3.0.x

Linux:
	Make sure you're in the project root, then type:
		mkdir build
		cd build
		cmake ..
		make
	
	If all goes well, you'll have a binary in there called turtle-demo. 
	To run the program, type:
		./turtle-demo

